    "title": "Front Office Manager - Oberoi Hotels - Top MNC",
    "description": "Grow your career with Oberoi Hotels! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Ludhiana team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Oberoi Hotels:\nOberoi Hotels is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Oberoi Hotels!",
